Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  站在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來不就好了  什麼時候來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.01,0:00:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到藤井君了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他剛剛回去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道你會來的話就讓他等等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話就能一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌君來做什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和藤井君…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.51,0:00:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.42,0:02:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是  應該是在echoes第一次見面時…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在戀愛上沒什麼經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也根本沒有想過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己都不明白自己的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也是  那個也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有過那樣的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在想起來  那都是對藤井君的感情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  從彌生小姐那裏拿到由綺的信後讓我確信了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撕了扔掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做還是人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼理奈會…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈看過信了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.55,0:03:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌生小姐說直接轉交了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌君又說是從理奈這裏得知的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.81,0:03:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌君  理奈  彌生小姐說的都不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我越來越不明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越愛往奇怪的地方去想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然知道不該去懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這根本毫無關聯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:04:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻好像能從冬彌君身上聞到彌生小姐香水的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是又覺得冬彌君好像隱瞞了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.75,0:04:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人都做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個是真的  哪個又是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人  騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都在騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.34,0:04:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌生小姐  藤井君都在騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想過說不定就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  不能那樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就像是在背叛理奈和冬彌君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡可能不那樣去想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但果然是猜中了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我像之前那樣  拜託他做我的助手了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才說想拜託的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請再次僱用我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去M3
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君他接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  只有那樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經遲了  由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君已經接受了我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想聽！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把我怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想聽…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打我吧  由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的喜歡藤井君的話就不要忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  用那雙手…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快鬆開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快鬆開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不了  打不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.46,0:06:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為理奈也是我最喜歡的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓偶像不惜傷害自己的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有那樣的戀愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君是由綺最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我卻把那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做個忍氣吞聲的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有忍氣吞聲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠永遠永遠等下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來都是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不回來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:07:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到死去  直到從這世界上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全相反呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  和由綺  藤井君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺和藤井君非常相似
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像兄妹一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.79,0:07:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不會放棄藤井君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話我也等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也並非被告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來路途會很漫長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就先以眼前的維納斯為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始努力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺也是  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定不參加維納斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和緒方先生這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是為了什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再說出這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就是我打你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:07:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我約好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後我們於公於私都是對手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了打敗我而努力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是提議  也不是商量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我做為前輩的最後的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服從吧  由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經這麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩人在車裏等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.81,0:08:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  又道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要送由綺一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別了  由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東央電視台嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長  由綺小姐來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌生小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能稍微兜一會風嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會影響明天的工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你保證今天再也不哭了  我就陪你去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開車了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:11:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人沒能振作起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就沒意義吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒方先生非常生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的生氣的話不會這樣就了事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天空出了點時間  去給理奈加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.47,0:11:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯繫晚了  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈很有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有雖然有點突然  但我要開始新的打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能給理奈做助手…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  拿畫去做擔保所以不在手上？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我待會兒再打過去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真準時啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天起請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  雖然我聽過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專輯  不怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零零散散  看不出主題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是小英的極限了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們這裏可行不通哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會交給專業的作家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我稍作保留吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:12:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫藤井
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的專屬助理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不承認
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我用自己的錢雇的  不會給你添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前那樣的任性是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪瑙小姐的…是叫夏子小姐吧  她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為瑪瑙說沒有那孩子就唱不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  沒有他的話就唱不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和事務所沒有任何關係  就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意不要引起誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時也不需要經紀人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  維納斯是瑪瑙出場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏也注意不要誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼當前我該做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:14:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛  現在瑪瑙正在錄專輯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫她和聲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是原來你哥哥的錄音室  知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你參加的話將會成為不錯的宣傳的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個全都要加進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  這半年間緒方理奈的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我和你所找到的東西  原原本本地錄進去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉匣一樣的專輯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是潘多拉的盒子  你覺得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天起要在一起了  請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們才是  請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經紀…  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是負責洞院沙莉衣的室町
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的那張單曲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經決定由瑪瑙小姐來寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從好的意義上來說  我們還是一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以誰的歌都能唱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈真是辛苦呢  顏色已經定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是哥哥的歌就唱不了  真辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那種事  我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…未成年嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實從上個月起就二十歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是推廣時說是十八歲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢  我記得…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從兩年前起就成年了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然已經不是秘密了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我還大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子  沙莉衣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概社長也知道她不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從櫻團的時候起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有察覺到的只有她本人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.81,0:16:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  已經察覺到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不聽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說絕不放棄  要單飛出道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某種意義上也許也是非常樂觀的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.70,0:16:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我就只會悲觀地注視現實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是她而是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想已經實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在內場辦了演唱會了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是該對神崎社長說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,職業歌手照現在這個樣子對她是沒好處的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個似乎就是我們所不懂的大人的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不出口的話  就只有替她加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:16:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來要去打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚報和青年報
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去的事情很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉理奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是找不到出租車
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在停在下面了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出租車？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過是租車子來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我沒有駕照  這種事還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  應該有簽約的公司吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓前台的人問了社長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為租車要花錢  所以好像不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  去把出租車退了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:09.44,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}理奈轉會的真相  前經紀人獨家專訪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在公會堂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點開始吧  讓我聽一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼辦吧  理奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難唱的話  改掉也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒說難唱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是旋律的銜接有點讓人不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵你在聽嗎  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:07.45,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嘎—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:12.06,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}救命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高潮前合唱的地方  第二小節的第三個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個人變成降調  這還是重做下比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏  也沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得缺少點味道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就刪掉好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話我來做和聲  再混入合唱裏怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:19:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照理奈喜歡的做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說在公會堂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.31,0:20:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去演唱會的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花束嗎  你是森川由綺的歌迷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.82,0:20:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的大人居然也會追星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.67,0:20:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像騙人的一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  像騙人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.05,0:21:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  能來聽一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.45,0:21:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.90,0:21:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我檢查一下麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說隨你便了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  那我就隨便了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.41,0:21:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在住在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊吹町…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.85,0:22:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.28,0:22:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒方先生  為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.72,0:22:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.99,0:24:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十頁
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.89,0:24:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛是盲目的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.83,0:24:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會這樣交談的戀人們
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.95,0:24:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是詩人  評論家  哲學家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.44,0:24:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,White  Album

